n16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1017308, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Mobasshir bin Abul Aziz narrates: I was available in the service of Imam Sadiq (a) when one of his Shias arrived and said: My life be sacrificed on you! I am destitute and need. Imam Sadiq (a) said: Wait until the arrival of Wednesday, keep fast on that day, then on the days of Thursday and Friday. On Friday, at the time of Zuhr, go to the terrace of your house, or towards a desert, such that you are not sighted by anyone, then perform the Ziyarat of the Holy Prophet (s); then offer two-unit prayer in that same place. Then sit in such a position that your leg touches the ground, then while facing the Qibla, place your right hand on the left hand and raise it towards the sky, then say…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Mobashshir bin Abdul Aziz kehte hai: Hazrat Imam Sadiq (a) ki khidmat mein haazir tha keh itne mein hamare as-haab mein se ek aaya aur kehne laga: Aap par qurbaan jaawu, mai faqeer hu kya karu? Hazrat ne us se farmaya: Roz-e-Chaar-shambe (Wednesday), Panch-shambe (Thursday) aur Juma (Friday) ko 3 din musalsal roza rakho, aur Roz-e-Juma Zohr ke waqt apne ghar ki chhat se ya aise baya-baan mein jahan tumhe koi na dekh sake, Rasool-e-Khuda (s) ki ziyarat padho aur phir 2 rakat namaz padho, phir qibla rukh ho kar dono zaanu ke bal (tashahud ki haalat mein) baiyth jaawo aur daayne (right) haath ko baayne (left) haath par rakh kar kaho…", "UrduDescription": "مبشر بن عبد العزیز کہتے ہیں: حصرت امام صادقؑ کی خدمت میں حاضر تھا کہ اتنے میں ہمارے اصحاب میں سے ایک آیا اور کہنے لگا: آپ پر قربان جاؤں، میں مقیر ہوں کیا کروں؟ حضرت نے اس سے فرمایا: رہز چارشنبہ(پدھ)، پانچشنبہ (جمعرات) اور جمعہ یہ ۳ دن روزہ رکھوں اور روز جمعہ ظہر کے وقت اپنے گھر کی چھت سے یا ایسے بیابان میں جہاں تمہیں کوئی نہ دیکھ سکے، رسول خداؐ کی زیارت پڑھو اور پھر ۲ رکعت نماز ادا کرو، پھر دونوں زانؤوں کے بل پیٹھ اؤ اس طرح کی زانو زمین سے لگے ہوئے ہوں اور قبلہ رخ ہو کر داہبے ہاتھ کو بائیں ہاتھ پر رکھو اور کہو۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "Arabic