ther than You, provide me with relief and ease of exit in my affair, and give me sustenance from where I reckon, and from where I don’t even reckon.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA ANTA ANTA, IN-QAT-A’R RAJAAA-O ILLAA MINKA, WA KHAABA-TIL AAMAALO ILLAA FEEKA, YAA SEQATA MAN LAA SEQATA LAHU, LAA SEQATA LEE GHAIRO-KA, IJ-A’L MIN AMREE FARAJAN, WAR-ZUQNEE MIN HAIYSO AH-TASEBO, WA MIN HAIYSO LAA AH-TASEBO.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اَنْتَ اَنْتَ، اِنْقَطْعَ الرَّجَائُ اِلَّا مِنْكَ، وَخَابَتِ الْآمَالُ اِلَّا فِیْكَ، یَا ثِقَۃَ مَنْ لَا ثِقَۃَ لَهٗ، لَا ثِقَۃَ لِیْ غَیْرُكَ، اِجْعَلْ مِنْ اَمْرِیْ فَرَجً، وَارْزُقْنِیْ مِنْ حَیْثُ اَحْتَسِبُ، وَمِنْ حَیْثُ لَا اَحْتَسِبُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13":